name: Terrifyingly Expensive Ellipse (Orchid)
description: The Terrifyingly Expensive Ellipse (Orchid)—also known as the 'TEEO’—is a 10000x10000 300dpi artwork by Optera featuring a small, orchid-colored ellipse at its center. It is not advised to collect this 1 of 1 piece unless you are terrifyingly wealthy.
